This paper discusses the use of knowledge graphs and graph databases, which are commonly studied in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of query languages for graph databases, which is a topic of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses graph pattern matching queries, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL) applications.
